# DMC13_GXTB_PROTOCOL dmc13-gxtb-spglib-reduced-v1
&GLOBAL
  PRINT_LEVEL LOW
  PROJECT ice_Ih_GXTB_gamma
  RUN_TYPE ENERGY
&END GLOBAL

&FORCE_EVAL
